And I'm human.

22:57.472 --> 23:01.356
I don't want to let myself get caught up in anything other than presenting the gospel.

23:01.857 --> 23:07.183
And sometimes I think you can get too big, too fast, and you forget why you're there.

23:07.784 --> 23:09.266
And I never want to forget why I'm there.

23:10.210 --> 23:11.812
Roger is an interesting man.

23:11.872 --> 23:18.381
He's a unique kind of person that works in the capital, the power center of the globe, let's just say.

23:19.723 --> 23:20.865
But he's not there for power.

23:21.626 --> 23:22.607
He's not there for money.

23:23.288 --> 23:26.212
He's not there for photo ops or even publicity.

23:26.232 --> 23:28.695
We're trying to give you publicity here.

23:28.755 --> 23:29.977
But you're very humble about it.

23:31.339 --> 23:33.442
What is the gospel of Jesus Christ?

23:33.542 --> 23:34.403
Why do you do this?

23:34.463 --> 23:36.926
There's somebody out there watching who doesn't know Jesus.

23:37.367 --> 23:38.108
Would you talk to them?

23:38.769 --> 23:39.570
Well, for me,

23:40.290 --> 23:41.992
It was like I was in the lowest place.

23:47.639 --> 23:49.121
But somebody shared who Christ was.

23:50.983 --> 24:07.764
And for me, it's understanding that here's a man who was God also, who left his God state, came down to be a human and was tortured, punished, and killed for me.

24:07.784 --> 24:09.586
Why would you not tell people about that?

24:12.322 --> 24:14.264
Because without Him, there's no telling where I'd be.

24:14.724 --> 24:15.385
I wouldn't be here.

24:16.246 --> 24:17.207
I wouldn't be talking to you.

24:18.628 --> 24:28.338
Because before we're saved, before we come to know Christ, you don't really get to see how bad you are.

24:28.639 --> 24:34.445
Because the devil puts you right around people that are a little worse than you, which makes you not feel so bad.

24:35.526 --> 24:39.570
But once the Lord took a hold of my heart and I gave my life to Him,

24:41.410 --> 24:42.752
He opened the eyes.

24:43.172 --> 24:45.095
He's like, man, I was not a good person.

24:45.896 --> 24:46.677
I should not be here.

24:46.757 --> 24:47.598
I should not be there.

24:48.159 --> 24:49.841
So I'll tell people that are searching.

24:52.205 --> 25:01.177
I never felt freer than the day I accepted Christ because everything that was pounding on me and hitting on me, it was gone.

25:02.379 --> 25:07.586
And I had somebody that I could turn to regardless of the situation.

25:08.627 --> 25:10.770
And he would listen and he would just

25:11.042 --> 25:12.204
love me for me.

25:13.385 --> 25:15.749
And then he puts people in your path.

25:17.151 --> 25:19.494
You know, it's funny how the Lord wants you to accept him.

25:20.616 --> 25:25.783
He's always putting people right when you need him.

25:25.803 --> 25:26.344
Wow.

25:26.364 --> 25:28.727
You know, you may not even see it coming.

25:28.747 --> 25:31.871
You don't even realize that you need that person.

25:31.892 --> 25:35.396
But the Lord knew before I was born and on that day I was going to need that person.

25:35.416 --> 25:36.498
And the Lord knew that

25:36.674 --> 25:43.545
Somebody out there would be watching this program on their television in their living room, not expecting to hear from you today.

25:44.928 --> 25:48.433
Would you just talk into the camera and just offer to pray with them?

25:48.794 --> 25:50.757
Maybe you could close our interview with the word of prayer.

25:50.998 --> 25:51.498
Absolutely.

25:52.119 --> 25:56.006
So, whatever you're going through, the Lord is there.

25:57.068 --> 25:58.189
You can always turn to Him.

25:59.031 --> 26:00.573
You can give Him everything.

26:00.593 --> 26:03.378
You don't have to hide anything because He sees it all anyway.

26:04.354 --> 26:05.376
So I want to pray for y'all.

26:05.396 --> 26:08.320
If there's anything that you need, lift it up to the Lord as I'm praying.

26:08.981 --> 26:09.782
Let him know you need him.

26:09.843 --> 26:15.712
If you don't know the Lord, don't let today go by without coming to know him in this prayer.

26:15.732 --> 26:17.394
Our Heavenly Father Lord, thank you for this time.

26:17.414 --> 26:19.698
Thank you for the privilege of being here.

26:20.259 --> 26:22.583
Lord, whoever's watching this, I'm going to lift them up to you now.

26:23.424 --> 26:27.530
Lord, there's somebody hurting in dire straits, looking for you.

26:28.151 --> 26:30.715
Lord, I ask that you would just send something to them.

26:31.256 --> 26:32.498
Draw them to you, Lord.

26:32.834 --> 26:35.657
Let today be the day they accept you as their Lord and Savior.

26:36.098 --> 26:37.940
Lord, watch over them, protect them.

26:37.960 --> 26:42.185
Lord, we thank You for watching over us and being with us.

26:42.225 --> 26:44.548
Lord, most of we thank You for dying for us.

26:46.410 --> 26:48.693
And Lord, just be with them, watch over them.

26:48.733 --> 26:49.754
You're precious name.

26:49.774 --> 26:51.456
Amen.

26:51.476 --> 26:53.298
Our guest has been Roger Roseberry.

26:53.318 --> 26:57.923
Their website is capitalfaithministries.com.

26:58.124 --> 27:00.146
Capitalfaith.com.

27:02.370 --> 27:04.173
capitalfaith.com.

27:04.193 --> 27:07.919
And that's with the T-O-L capitalfaith.com.

27:08.279 --> 27:09.261
Roger, it's great to meet you.

27:09.281 --> 27:10.322
Thanks for coming on the program.

27:10.362 --> 27:10.663
Yes, sir.

27:10.683 --> 27:11.023
Thank you.

27:11.704 --> 27:12.426
I'm Dr. Chaps.

27:14.088 --> 27:17.293
Let's continue in a spirit of prayer.

27:17.353 --> 27:20.378
We want you to support capitalfaith.com today.

27:20.999 --> 27:27.449
